{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWith:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"}]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"tags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set during registration.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags)."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Combines push notification registration with tag assignment in a single operation.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is more efficient than calling registerForPushNotifications and setTags separately,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as tags are sent to the server along with the registration request."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method when you have user attributes available at the time of registration,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as during onboarding or after user authentication."}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register with user attributes after sign-up:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class SignUpCoordinator {","","    func completeSignUp(user: User, source: SignUpSource) {","        let registrationTags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_source\": source.analyticsValue,","            \"signup_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"interests\": user.selectedInterests,","            \"language\": Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\",","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(with: registrationTags)","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(user.email)","    }","}","","extension Bundle {","    var appVersion: String {","        infoDictionary?[\"CFBundleShortVersionString\"] as? String ?? \"unknown\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pu